論文名稱(中)
應用WiMAX技術於遠距醫療照護之概念性驗證研究-以某醫學中心為例

論文名稱(英)
WiMAX Technology in the Proof of Conceptand Research of Long-distance Healthcare

檔案

etd-0211109-111253.pdf

本電子全文僅授權使用者為學術研究之目的，進行個人非營利性質之檢索、閱讀、列印。
        			 請遵守中華民國著作權法之相關規定，切勿任意重製、散佈、改作、轉貼、播送，以免觸法。

論文使用權限
校內校外均不公開

論文種類
碩士論文


論文語文別 / 頁數
中文 / 51

統計
已被瀏覽 2595 次，被下載 4 次

關鍵字(中)
WiMAX
遠距醫療照護

關鍵字(英)
Telecare
WiMAX


摘要(中)
隨著全球人口高齡化結構社會來臨，資訊通訊和醫療科技的快速進步，世界各國無不積極推動以資訊、通訊科技結合醫療技術以遠距的方式，來建構e化、行動化 (M)、U化（Ubiquitous)等無所不在的新型態健康與照護服務模式。行動遠距照護服務係以不涉及診療行為，而是提供照護、諮詢服務的遠距醫療服務，可以免去一些長期的慢性病患，必須往返醫院、住家之間的舟車勞頓，更讓醫生能夠充分掌握病患的日常狀況。而以WiMAX無線網路技術應用於行動醫療照護，更有助提昇長期照護服務與遠距照護服務的品質與滿意度的效益。行動照護的特點，在於利用網路的快速傳輸與寬頻無線的行動力，在需要服務的時候，藉由即時資訊的提供讓醫療資源可以打破現有的服務疆界，在提昇全民照護品質的同時亦可將珍貴的資源做最有效的應用，達到預防、診斷、治療等成效。本研究從「新型態無線網路技術、醫療行動照護、遠距服務」三方面整合構面，以資訊安全的「機密性」、「完整性」與「可用性」等三項資料安全評估條件為基礎，提供完整服務平臺，並且架構網路安全機制，有效降低網站安全威脅的風險，達到提高新一代醫療化無線資訊平臺安全之目的。

摘要(英)
Approaching along with the structural aging-society in global population, information correspondence and medical technology progress fast that is result in the newly healthcare patterns are constructed for information and technological correspondence with electronic (E)-, mobile (M)- and ubiquitous (U)- style of long-range medical techniques that impel positively in various countries. Instead of diagnosis, active telecare service provides for healthcare and consultation with telemedicine. Doctor enables know well about routine condition of sickness as to exempt long-term chronic patients from depleting time between home and hospital. Applies by WiMAX wireless network technology in the active healthcare can helpful to promote benefit in quality and approval level of long-term telecare service. The characteristic of Mobile Healthcare Service is including motion strength lies in network speedy transmission and wireless broadband. According to it, immediate information makes medical resources to be possible to break existing service border. While enhancing healthcare quality of general public, it also to be possible to do that precious resource effectively achieves outcomes in prevention, diagnosis and treatment. This study is constructed from three categories about newly wireless network technology, active healthcare and telemedicine. Based on three evaluative items of information security about confidentiality, integrity and utility, it provides complete service platform of medical information system as well as constructs network safety mechanism. In addition, it decreases effectively risk of website security threat, and achieves to raise goal of new generation in medical service of wireless information of platform security.

